[I] Library for creating events

[T] EventViews is part of KDE PIM (Personal Information Management), that
[T] provides tools for managing calendars, tasks, emails and other
[T] organizational needs. The Library deals with rendering and managing
[T] calendar events and tasks in KDE applications.

